d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果區冇毓民(但又唔想投陳雲)，所以咪投左人社既長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同本民青有私怨?<br />\n定係唔支持港獨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同本民青政冇私怨<br />\n2008年開始慣性投開梁國雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n總之投青政(梁頌恆), 雖然青政2子已經俾支共dq</blockquote><br />\n雖然佢地表現真係令人失望<br />\n但至少成個陣營無人割蓆<br />\n淨係呢點都令我無後悔過幫梁頌恆助選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會冇？容癌班人選前endorse完本民青就當正自己民意代表咁周圍撩起火頭，到梁游被DQ就個個扮晒唔識佢地。講到尾又係投機份子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48768e86ba91f021dd34525a2ff81aa79df82bfb","tid":274054,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但就投左俾5號既梁國雄，國際大中華膠同 &ldquo;社會主義左翼&rdquo;(不過係收資本主義陣營肥佬黎錢)既長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果區冇毓民(但又唔想投陳雲)，所以咪投左人社既長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同本民青有私怨?<br />\n定係唔支持港獨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同本民青政冇私怨<br />\n2008年開始慣性投開梁國雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n總之投青政(梁頌恆), 雖然青政2子已經俾支共dq</blockquote><br />\n雖然佢地表現真係令人失望<br />\n但至少成個陣營無人割蓆<br />\n淨係呢點都令我無後悔過幫梁頌恆助選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會冇？容癌班人選前endorse完本民青就當正自己民意代表咁周圍撩起火頭，到梁游被DQ就個個扮晒唔識佢地。講到尾又係投機份子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊真係組織聯盟嘅人<br />\n<br />\n但我見容癌佢地班人仲有互like fb post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c965bbca9a9bc253